051-599 bewerbung@analytical-software.de https://www.linkedin.com/in/irena-marasek-656458aa/ https://www.xing.com/profile/Irena_Marasek/cv</p>\n<p></p><p><b>Kai Brodmann</b><br>\nBereichsleiter Data Science &amp; Business Intelligence</p></div>"}
